name: Apartments at Palanga

name: Apartments near Baltic sea
description:
An inexpensive place to stay in Vilnius.

 It's not a specially rented apartment: I simply rent one room in a three-room flat where I live and work myself and will be happy to see guests from around the world. The building is 200 m away from the main street which guarantees peace and quiet at all times.

description: The apartment is suitable for a couples or for a single travelers. It is very cozy and comfortable space, fully designed and furnished by me.
